Recap of OOP Concepts

Class â†’ har problem ek class me solve.

Attributes/Properties â†’ jaise self.text, self.people, self.number.

Methods â†’ count_words, make_change, calculate, etc.

Inheritance â†’ HandheldCalculator â†’ SimpleCalculator se inherit.

