ğŸ“ Explanation (Easy Language)

Class: har problem ke liye ek class banayi.

Properties (Attributes): data store karne ke liye (jaise self.text, self.number, etc.).

Methods: functions jo object kaam karte hain (count_words, make_change, etc.).

Inheritance: HandheldCalculator â†’ inherits from SimpleCalculator (uses super() to reuse code).

Encapsulation: har class ka apna data internally handle hota hai.

Polymorphism: override kiya calculate method ko ek aur class me (advanced concept).